precis:
Enactment of the SPECIAL DUTY AREA PENSION ORDER - which repeals and
reenacts, in an identical manner, the Order made under Apropriation Act
No. 10, 1964, except for the addition of East Timor to the list of areas
designated as a "Special Service Area".
